{"tid":769296,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"京都妖怪計程車","createTime":"2018-08-06T05:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T06:43:28.000Z","uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f32bfa86709f2a6999935769640f2e025100f5b","tid":769296,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:29:27.000Z","msg":"「京都妖怪計程車」已於日前上路，打算在炎炎夏日為人們沁涼身心。乘客能夠一面在車內聽著怪談，一面遊覽故事相關景點。而坐在副駕駛座上的妖怪「滑頭鬼」人偶，雖然一副怪裡怪氣的模樣，卻也令人感覺討喜。<br />\n<br />\n　　妖怪計程車是由興進TAXI負責營運。恐怖傳說與怪談為千年古都的獨有特色，如今仍流傳於府內各地，而業者便是看準這點。「妖怪傳說探訪之旅或許也有市場需求。」他們帶著這樣的念頭實現了此一企劃。現年57歲的董事濱田典亨表示:「歡迎來到魔界之旅。希望乘客們感到涼爽，就算只有氣氛也好。」<br />\n<br />\n　　包括京都市內的寺廟等處，將帶領乘客遊覽5個有妖怪故事流傳的地點。乘客能一面搭著車，一面在車內聽著下一個探訪地的相關怪談。<br />\n<br />\n　　妖怪計程車從6月起上路，8月份已連日排入預約。雖然多為團體客，也有來自府外的女性單獨搭乘。不知是否為了體驗「這裡可能有妖怪」的氣氛，目前仍沒人想在白天搭乘。<br />\n<br />\n　　妖怪計程車將持續至10月15日，全程約4小時。4~6人座的一般車輛收費2萬400日圓(約合新台幣5680元)，9人座大型包車為2萬4000日圓(約合新台幣6680元)；停車費、參拜費及收費道路費用則額外收取。須在搭乘日的2天前預約，詳情請洽+81-75-681-4481。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://asahichinese-f.com/photo/15373427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasahichinese-f.com%2Fphoto%2F15373427&d=oOZMTXzW7vfu8itstuCjnQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=9008a664\" target=\"_blank\">https://asahichinese-f.com/photo/15373427</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://public.potaufeu.asahi.com/2d3b-p/picture/13310263/3ac9c613d5826587c8c3ebf431a27a68_640px.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.potaufeu.asahi.com%2F2d3b-p%2Fpicture%2F13310263%2F3ac9c613d5826587c8c3ebf431a27a68_640px.jpg&h=3886fdc2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26ffe4a6dacfb7c56016dabedd74463b9dd1f94a","tid":769296,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27642d154b5aa201c78582550bbb9a7875d61e04","tid":769296,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:43:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">計程車</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}